{"tid":2203161,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃毓民公開呼籲鄺俊宇許智峰退出民主黨：唔好比民主黨d惡行燒哂自己過去一年既光環","createTime":"2020-09-15T06:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T08:44:22.000Z","uid":157483,"like":35,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6bea1824c8dd6ff5c140b8c3e3abf02f02338dd8","tid":2203161,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=1L-ccf5kyAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1L-ccf5kyAw&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=c2992fac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=1L-ccf5kyAw</a><br />\n<br />\n8:35開始<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民：我溫馨提示或者叫警告，你鄺俊宇許智峰兩個仲似返個人既民主黨年輕人，一定要退出民主黨，同埋拒絕加入臨立會，如果唔係下屆有選舉你死硬。<br />\n你肯做既話下屆一定做票王！我而家係度講既。你過去一年抗爭出黎咁多次，又比警察打又比人告咁多罪，你唔好比民主黨攬炒，燒返你既光環。<br />\n其實你許智峰當初搶手機案，民主黨班老野已經想踢鳩走你嫁啦！係見你呢一年個勢咁勁，焗住要比你選姐嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>有link有比時間 咪撚再屈我fake news五毛pr屌你老尾</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"268cc9f99f42df39e9ab4dc4f70b1c3cbcc76ae7","tid":2203161,"uid":143343,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:56:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c64d6ca39c3dd934559c48da1df89ad0228109a9","tid":2203161,"uid":143343,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88c7354d829364c8ec506fd5537214e5ab2d3fa2","tid":2203161,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fe84d859ba6278a8db169b45618dd44c255f12","tid":2203161,"uid":316612,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"好快又有泛民打手入黎屌分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji